  Cause.isFailType(cause) && cause.error instanceof SoulLoadError
    ? Effect.fail(cause.error) // preserve the existing message
    : Effect.fail(new SoulLoadError({ message: "...", cause })),
);
```

Then the tests could assert specific message content like `toContain("Error parsing soul manifest")` and truly validate each remapping path.

